                        <div class="card-body p-4">
                            <p class="small mb-2 mt-0">Date</p>
                            <h5 class="card-title fs-4 fw-900 text-secondary">Barcelona</h5>
                            <p class="card-text my-3">Consequat tempor incididunt minim quis tempor qui pariatur commodo aute cillum in. Consectetur excepteur ipsum duis culpa cupidatat aute.</p>
